  * Prior experience leading a team in a diverse cultural environment in a mining context is desirable. 
  * Proficient in English with excellent verbal, written communication and public speaking skills. 
  * Proven track record for the delivery of project objectives and established targets 
  * Self-motivated with the ability to work under pressure and autonomously. 
  
Desirable  

